{"body":"[{\"data\":1,\"prerenderedAt\":260},[\"ShallowReactive\",2],{\"navigation\":3,\"blog-page\":22,\"blogs\":32},[4],{\"title\":5,\"path\":6,\"stem\":7,\"children\":8,\"page\":21},\"Blog\",\"\\u002Fblog\",\"blog\",[9,13,17],{\"title\":10,\"path\":11,\"stem\":12},\"用 Nuxt 初始化个人简历与技术博客\",\"\\u002Fblog\\u002Fbuilding-my-personal-site-with-nuxt\",\"blog\\u002Fbuilding-my-personal-site-with-nuxt\",{\"title\":14,\"path\":15,\"stem\":16},\"前端工程化笔记：从可运行到可维护\",\"\\u002Fblog\\u002Ffrontend-engineering-notes\",\"blog\\u002Ffrontend-engineering-notes\",{\"title\":18,\"path\":19,\"stem\":20},\"项目复盘模板：把经历写成作品\",\"\\u002Fblog\\u002Fproject-review-template\",\"blog\\u002Fproject-review-template\",false,{\"id\":23,\"title\":24,\"body\":25,\"description\":26,\"extension\":27,\"links\":25,\"meta\":28,\"navigation\":29,\"path\":6,\"seo\":30,\"stem\":7,\"__hash__\":31},\"pages\\u002Fblog.yml\",\"技术博客\",null,\"记录技术实践、项目复盘、学习笔记和对软件工程的长期思考。\",\"yml\",{},true,{\"title\":24,\"description\":26},\"h8Pzd7lbq2oYdZtu-SGGv7CD1UScFO9Erk27BRzsHqA\",[33,114,207],{\"id\":34,\"title\":10,\"author\":35,\"body\":40,\"date\":106,\"description\":107,\"extension\":108,\"image\":109,\"meta\":110,\"minRead\":111,\"navigation\":29,\"path\":11,\"seo\":112,\"stem\":12,\"__hash__\":113},\"blog\\u002Fblog\\u002Fbuilding-my-personal-site-with-nuxt.md\",{\"name\":36,\"description\":37,\"avatar\":38},\"你的名字\",\"前端 \\u002F 全栈开发者\",{\"src\":39,\"alt\":36},\"https:\\u002F\\u002Fimages.unsplash.com\\u002Fphoto-1701615004837-40d8573b6652?q=80&w=1480&auto=format&fit=crop\",{\"type\":41,\"value\":42,\"toc\":99},\"minimark\",[43,47,52,55,58,93,96],[44,45,46],\"p\",{},\"这个站点使用 Nuxt、Nuxt UI 和 Nuxt Content 构建。它不是一个单纯的静态简历，而是一个可以持续更新的个人内容系统：简历负责说明“我是谁”，项目页负责说明“我做过什么”，博客负责沉淀“我如何思考和解决问题”。\",[48,49,51],\"h2\",{\"id\":50},\"为什么选择-nuxt\",\"为什么选择 Nuxt\",[44,53,54],{},\"Nuxt 对内容型站点很友好，路由、SEO、图片、组件系统和构建流程都比较完整。配合 Nuxt Content，可以直接用 Markdown 管理文章，用 YAML 管理首页、项目和简历信息。\",[48,56,57],{\"id\":57},\"当前结构\",[59,60,61,69,75,81,87],\"ul\",{},[62,63,64,68],\"li\",{},[65,66,67],\"code\",{},\"content\\u002Findex.yml\",\"：首页文案、工作经历和 FAQ\",[62,70,71,74],{},[65,72,73],{},\"content\\u002Fabout.yml\",\"：在线简历正文\",[62,76,77,80],{},[65,78,79],{},\"content\\u002Fprojects\\u002F*.yml\",\"：项目作品\",[62,82,83,86],{},[65,84,85],{},\"content\\u002Fblog\\u002F*.md\",\"：博客文章\",[62,88,89,92],{},[65,90,91],{},\"app\\u002Fapp.config.ts\",\"：头像、邮箱、社交链接和页脚信息\",[48,94,95],{\"id\":95},\"后续计划\",[44,97,98],{},\"下一步可以继续补充真实头像、真实项目、文章分类、标签页和部署配置。等内容稳定后，再根据自己的视觉偏好调整色彩、字体和首页图片。\",{\"title\":100,\"searchDepth\":101,\"depth\":101,\"links\":102},\"\",2,[103,104,105],{\"id\":50,\"depth\":101,\"text\":51},{\"id\":57,\"depth\":101,\"text\":57},{\"id\":95,\"depth\":101,\"text\":95},\"2026-06-09\",\"记录这个站点的技术选型、内容结构和后续可扩展方向。\",\"md\",\"https:\\u002F\\u002Fimages.unsplash.com\\u002Fphoto-1498050108023-c5249f4df085?q=80&w=1472&auto=format&fit=crop\",{},5,{\"title\":10,\"description\":107},\"7GKQwCl4p0hsKZpxbzFT6B4UqgFwzxYO1jE5RdjdgVw\",{\"id\":115,\"title\":14,\"author\":116,\"body\":118,\"date\":200,\"description\":201,\"extension\":108,\"image\":202,\"meta\":203,\"minRead\":204,\"navigation\":29,\"path\":15,\"seo\":205,\"stem\":16,\"__hash__\":206},\"blog\\u002Fblog\\u002Ffrontend-engineering-notes.md\",{\"name\":36,\"description\":37,\"avatar\":117},{\"src\":39,\"alt\":36},{\"type\":41,\"value\":119,\"toc\":195},[120,123,126,137,140,143,178,181,184,191],[44,121,122],{},\"一个项目能跑起来只是第一步。真正长期可用的项目，需要在依赖管理、代码规范、类型检查、构建验证和部署流程上保持基本秩序。\",[48,124,125],{\"id\":125},\"依赖管理\",[44,127,128,129,132,133,136],{},\"依赖应该尽量统一包管理器，并把锁文件提交到仓库。本项目使用 \",[65,130,131],{},\"pnpm\",\"，对应的锁文件是 \",[65,134,135],{},\"pnpm-lock.yaml\",\"。新增依赖时，优先确认是否已有框架内置能力或项目已有工具可以复用。\",[48,138,139],{\"id\":139},\"代码质量\",[44,141,142],{},\"建议每次提交前至少运行：\",[144,145,149],\"pre\",{\"className\":146,\"code\":147,\"language\":148,\"meta\":100,\"style\":100},\"language-bash shiki shiki-themes material-theme-lighter material-theme material-theme-palenight\",\"pnpm lint\\npnpm typecheck\\npnpm build\\n\",\"bash\",[65,150,151,163,170],{\"__ignoreMap\":100},[152,153,156,159],\"span\",{\"class\":154,\"line\":155},\"line\",1,[152,157,131],{\"class\":158},\"sBMFI\",[152,160,162],{\"class\":161},\"sfazB\",\" lint\\n\",[152,164,165,167],{\"class\":154,\"line\":101},[152,166,131],{\"class\":158},[152,168,169],{\"class\":161},\" typecheck\\n\",[152,171,173,175],{\"class\":154,\"line\":172},3,[152,174,131],{\"class\":158},[152,176,177],{\"class\":161},\" build\\n\",[44,179,180],{},\"小项目也需要这三类检查。它们能提前暴露格式问题、类型问题和生产构建问题，避免上线时才发现错误。\",[48,182,183],{\"id\":183},\"内容维护\",[44,185,186,187,190],{},\"博客和项目数据放在 \",[65,188,189],{},\"content\",\" 目录中，这让内容维护不必侵入页面组件。写文章时只需要复制一篇 Markdown，修改 frontmatter 和正文即可。\",[192,193,194],\"style\",{},\"html pre.shiki code .sBMFI, html code.shiki .sBMFI{--shiki-light:#E2931D;--shiki-default:#FFCB6B;--shiki-dark:#FFCB6B}html pre.shiki code .sfazB, html code.shiki .sfazB{--shiki-light:#91B859;--shiki-default:#C3E88D;--shiki-dark:#C3E88D}html .light .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-light);background: var(--shiki-light-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-light-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-light-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-light-text-decoration);}html.light .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-light);background: var(--shiki-light-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-light-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-light-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-light-text-decoration);}html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .dark .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-dark);background: var(--shiki-dark-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-dark-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-dark-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-dark-text-decoration);}html.dark .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-dark);background: var(--shiki-dark-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-dark-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-dark-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-dark-text-decoration);}\",{\"title\":100,\"searchDepth\":101,\"depth\":101,\"links\":196},[197,198,199],{\"id\":125,\"depth\":101,\"text\":125},{\"id\":139,\"depth\":101,\"text\":139},{\"id\":183,\"depth\":101,\"text\":183},\"2026-06-08\",\"整理个人项目中常见的工程化检查点，包括依赖、规范、构建、部署和复盘。\",\"https:\\u002F\\u002Fimages.unsplash.com\\u002Fphoto-1515879218367-8466d910aaa4?q=80&w=1469&auto=format&fit=crop\",{},6,{\"title\":14,\"description\":201},\"OTjOXg2wd-337TA4wmOFXQYVoafnKvwOqfLot2JRd4Q\",{\"id\":208,\"title\":18,\"author\":209,\"body\":211,\"date\":253,\"description\":254,\"extension\":108,\"image\":255,\"meta\":256,\"minRead\":257,\"navigation\":29,\"path\":19,\"seo\":258,\"stem\":20,\"__hash__\":259},\"blog\\u002Fblog\\u002Fproject-review-template.md\",{\"name\":36,\"description\":37,\"avatar\":210},{\"src\":39,\"alt\":36},{\"type\":41,\"value\":212,\"toc\":246},[213,216,219,222,225,228,231,234,237,240,243],[44,214,215],{},\"好的项目展示不只是截图和技术栈列表，更重要的是说明问题、约束、决策和结果。下面是一套可以反复复用的复盘结构。\",[48,217,218],{\"id\":218},\"背景\",[44,220,221],{},\"这个项目为什么要做？目标用户是谁？业务或技术上的关键问题是什么？\",[48,223,224],{\"id\":224},\"职责\",[44,226,227],{},\"你负责了哪些部分？是独立完成，还是负责某个模块？是否包含需求分析、设计、开发、测试、上线或维护？\",[48,229,230],{\"id\":230},\"技术方案\",[44,232,233],{},\"说明主要技术栈、架构选择、数据流、组件划分和关键依赖。不要只列名词，要解释为什么这样选。\",[48,235,236],{\"id\":236},\"难点与取舍\",[44,238,239],{},\"记录最有价值的部分：哪些问题不确定？有哪些方案被放弃？最终为什么选择当前方案？\",[48,241,242],{\"id\":242},\"结果\",[44,244,245],{},\"尽量用具体结果收尾，例如性能指标、上线范围、用户反馈、维护成本变化，或者你从中学到的方法。\",{\"title\":100,\"searchDepth\":101,\"depth\":101,\"links\":247},[248,249,250,251,252],{\"id\":218,\"depth\":101,\"text\":218},{\"id\":224,\"depth\":101,\"text\":224},{\"id\":230,\"depth\":101,\"text\":230},{\"id\":236,\"depth\":101,\"text\":236},{\"id\":242,\"depth\":101,\"text\":242},\"2026-06-07\",\"给个人项目和工作项目准备的一套复盘结构，方便写进作品集和博客。\",\"https:\\u002F\\u002Fimages.unsplash.com\\u002Fphoto-1552664730-d307ca884978?q=80&w=1470&auto=format&fit=crop\",{},4,{\"title\":18,\"description\":254},\"sxDmkIag5QY0I0RoGw0ur-jY1UWWjMd9EZ1yNQZ-zGk\",1781460014670]","statusCode":200,"statusMessage":"","headers":{"content-type":"application/json;charset=utf-8","x-powered-by":"Nuxt"}}